Package: phanspeed
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: all
Maintainer: asuramaya <asuramaya@users.noreply.github.com>
Depends: python3, systemd
Recommends: gnome-shell, nvidia-smi
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/asuramaya/phanspeed
Description: Dell thermal/fan control daemon + GNOME Quick Settings pill
 PhanSpeed drives the working thermal levers on locked-down Dell laptops
 (Precision/XPS): the ACPI platform_profile, Intel RAPL CPU power caps, HWP
 energy-performance preference, and an emergency thermal failsafe. It includes a
 closed-loop power auto-tuner and a GNOME Shell Quick Settings pill, plus an
 optional self-updater. Pure Python standard library; no pip dependencies.
